{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/the-odin-project/top-learn-variables-and-operators/learn-variables-and-operators-lesson-b","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":[],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"top-learn-variables-and-operators","challengeType":15,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Možete razmotriti parametre kao podatke \"kontejnera za skladištenje\" u vašem kodu.</p>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/odin-project/variables-and-operators/top-learn-variables-and-operators.png\" alt='the concept of variables in coding as boxes labeled \"birthday\" that store and provide access to data, specifically a date \"16-09-2003\"'>\n<p>Kriterijum je \"imenovano skladište\" podataka. Možete koristiti kriterijume za skladištenje resursa, gostiju i drugih podataka.</p>\n<p>Da biste kreirali parametar u JavaScript, koristite ključnu reč <code>let</code>.</p>\n<p>Sledeće kreira (drugim rečima: objavljuje) parametar sa imenom \"message\":</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">let message;\n</code></pre>\n<p>Sada, možete uneti podatke u njega koristeći operater raspršivanja <code>=</code>:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">let message;\n\n// store the string 'Hello' in the variable named message\nmessage = 'Hello'; \n</code></pre>\n<p>Radi sažetosti, možete kombinovati deklaraciju parametra i dodelu vrednosti u jednoj liniji:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">let message = 'Hello';\n</code></pre>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"Odin","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/the-odin-project/top-learn-variables-and-operators/learn-variables-and-operators-lesson-b"},"questions":[{"text":"<p>Koja je svrha upotrebe ključne reči <code>let</code> unutar JavaScript?</p>","answers":[{"answer":"<p>Izvršiti aritmetičke operacije.</p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Objavi nepromenljivu vrednost.</p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Deklarisati parametar koji može da skladišti podatke, čija je vrednost dodeljiva i menjajuća.</p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Kreirati funkciju.</p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null}],"solution":3}],"scene":null,"superBlock":"the-odin-project","tests":[],"title":"Naučite o parametrima i funkcionisanju B","transcript":null,"translationPending":false,"videoId":null,"videoLocaleIds":null}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/the-odin-project/#top-learn-variables-and-operators","dashedName":"learn-variables-and-operators-lesson-b","certification":"the-odin-project","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"the-odin-project","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"top-learn-variables-and-operators","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/the-odin-project/top-learn-variables-and-operators/learn-variables-and-operators-lesson-c","prevChallengePath":"/learn/the-odin-project/top-learn-variables-and-operators/learn-variables-and-operators-lesson-a","id":"65e18d61500d930ce8ed90a5","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":15,"challengeFiles":[]}},"id":"/learn/the-odin-project/top-learn-variables-and-operators/learn-variables-and-operators-lesson-b"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}